• Elon Musk is an authorized biography of businessman Elon Musk. The book was written by Walter Isaacson, a former executive at CNN, TIME and the Aspen Institute who had previously written best-selling biographies of Benjamin Franklin, Albert Einstein, Steve Jobs and Leonardo da Vinci.

• Elon Musk is the owner of multiple companies, the wealthiest individual in the world, and a former US government employee.
